    {
      "name": "Make a safety plan. ",
      "description": "Help the person develop a set of steps he or she promises to follow during a suicidal crisis. It should identify any triggers that may lead to a suicidal crisis, such as an anniversary of a loss, alcohol, or stress from relationships. Also include contact numbers for the person\u0027s doctor or therapist, as well as friends and family members who will help in an emergency.",
